{"title":"难忘的时辰","authors":["易仁寰"],"dates":[{"year":1999,"month":12,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"难忘的时辰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"易仁寰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"童年，我站在珠海海滨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放飞一只龙形的风筝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风筝飞呀，飞呀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞到澳门上空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一阵风刮断线绳，风筝落在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对面的树丛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我想去摘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却进不去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"澳门之门……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长大后，我常到珠海海滨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把那首《七子之歌》朗诵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一阵风吹来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我听到对面的和声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们互相招手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"离得那样近"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但一堵四百年的墙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隔断了骨肉之情……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一年又一年，岁月的风雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"染白了我们的双鬓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天我站在珠海海滨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"温馨的春风使我忘却了年龄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看，一朵硕大的莲花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放飞在蔚蓝色的天空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莲香弥漫热土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"簇拥着金黄色的五星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，喜泪横流，血乳交融"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此刻都融入神州之梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1999年12月20日，历史的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时钟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将记住这个难忘的时辰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是一个民族"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一段屈辱史的终结"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国———将永远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"告别肢解之痛！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}